metadata.name: n Forms #102
metadata.description:
Hand-scrawled documentation of abstract structures. A journal from another realm.

Press 's' to save an image while in full-screen mode.

If you want to increase the resolution of the saved image, add e.g. &size=2000 after the live/fullscreen view URL to render the canvas at that specific pixel width (default = browser sized). This will be dependent on your system specifications, but outputs of up to 8000px wide, or above, should be possible.

Usually loads best in Chrome

metadata.name: A Distant Memory #103
metadata.description:
A distant memory of trees, buildings and the old village. Once a moment, the memory is illuminated by a beam of light, which gives me the insight of this work.

--------------------

This is an abstract generation made by pure code.

--------------------

In live mode, press 's' or 'S' to save a high resolution png.

Please be patient with drawing process (it'll take one minute in my computer).
This is my last artwork in 2022. I hope you like this work.

Endlessworld 2022

metadata.name: Flossom #235
metadata.description: This work is a research of flow fields, exploring generative art forms and colors. It uses various drawing methods, randomized color palettes, and layers of patterns to add multiple dimensions of variety to the work. Willing to create a visual blossom.

metadata.name: A Less Traveled Path #114
metadata.description:
"I shall be telling this with a sigh
Somewhere ages and ages hence:
Two roads diverged in a wood, and I—
I took the one less traveled by,
And that has made all the difference."

- Robert Frost, The Road Not Taken



=========

Controls:
[1] set resolution to 1024x1024 (default)
[2] set resolution to 2048x2048 
[3] set resolution to 4096x4096
[0] set resolution to window size (might help on lower end computers)

[c] capture a screenshot at rendered resolution


Made with cables.gl, a node-based webgl environment
XALTED 2022

metadata.name: Shifted Blocks #236
metadata.description:
The art is programmatically drawn using basic shapes, math, random using p5js.

To save image:

press '0' || 'd' to save image is default quality
press '1' || 's' to save image as '613x775px'
press '2' || 'm' to save image as '735x930px'
press '3' to save image as '883x1116px'
press '4' || 'p' to save image as '1059x1339px'
press '5' to save image as '1271x1607px'
press '6' to save image as '1525x1928px'
press '7' || 'h' to save image as '1831x2314px'

press 'f' to see art in full screen.

created by: https://twitter.com/mrmecroni or NotaArtist

metadata.name: Entangled shapes #18
metadata.description:
This project was born from an experiment that consists in arranging shapes in a random way by drawing the places where they overlap. To describe this superposition, the sides of the shapes are progressively reduced and if a part of the outline is inscribed in the other shape then it is drawn. 

In fine, a shape needs the other shapes to be described.
I see in this relationship a metaphor of our own existence as human beings where each one defines itself in relation to the others.


Controls in live mode
You can access a controls window by clicking on the sketch.
You can also control the sketch with the keyboard:
[r] restarts the animation.
[d] allows to download a PNG.
[1][2][3][4] changes the scale of the canvas and the PNG.

Note
This work is part of the Hybrid series, to learn more open the link available in the control window.

Artist
Nicolas Lebrun | Twitter: @nclslbrn

metadata.name: GEN XYZ Das Occult #712
metadata.description:
A 10k Generative Profile Pic collection
GEN XYZ Das Occult - by culla - @tamccullough

move over cryptopunks
there is a new group on the scene

100% code - not an image composition

A bunch of common palettes
A selection of rare palettes
And a smaller set of ultra rare palettes
However, rarity will be based on what combinations the code produces

The majority of tokens will not have a special trait
However your token might have one or even multiple special traits
But, be aware that only the last special trait added will be listed in the features

Even then, look closely, because not all aspects of the canvas are included in the features. Collectors should still look closely and choose what they like when buying on secondary.

Which team are you on? X or O?

follow culla on twitter for updates. Or maybe __acolyte__

If the non reserved tokens mint out quickly, Access List mints will have 24 hours to mint reserves assigned to those wallets

Thank you for supporting an emerging artist in the generative art space

Access List reserves were given to holders of the following PFP collections created by culla
2x for each Basqunk held
1x for each Inkspunk, TwoFourQunk, V0iD, DeeManz, Punkasso and CR0$$KULL
You would have needed to transfer the above tokens to your mint wallet at the time of the snapshot

share your tokens on social media with #genxyznft
Made with love by culla using p5.js
